    {
      "id": "client_conn_box", "type": "rectangle", "x": 60, "y": 240, "width": 400, "height": 260,
      "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#1971c2", "backgroundColor": "#dbe4ff",
      "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 2, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "index": "a4",
      "roundness": { "type": 3 }, "seed": 5001, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 5002,
      "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": [{"id": "text_clientconn", "type": "text"}],
      "updated": 1774700000000, "link": null, "locked": false
    },
    {
      "id": "text_clientconn", "type": "text", "x": 65, "y": 250, "width": 390, "height": 240,
      "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e", "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "index": "a4a", "roundness": null,
      "seed": 5003, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 5004, "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null, "updated": 1774700000000, "link": null, "locked": false,
      "text": "ClientConn  (one per connected client)\n\n┌─ Connection ──────────────────────────┐\n│  socketFd    (UDS / named pipe)       │\n│  shmFd       (shared memory region)   │\n│  txRing      (server → client, 256K)  │\n│  rxRing      (client → server, 256K)  │\n└───────────────────────────────────────┘\n\n  receiverThread   (reads rxRing)\n  sendMutex        (serializes txRing writes)\n  handlerMutex     (guards RunLoop dispatch)\n  dead flag        (atomic, marks for reaping)\n\n⚠ txRing is SPSC — sendMutex MUST be held\n  for sendResponse() AND sendNotify()",
      "originalText": "ClientConn  (one per connected client)\n\n┌─ Connection ──────────────────────────┐\n│  socketFd    (UDS / named pipe)       │\n│  shmFd       (shared memory region)   │\n│  txRing      (server → client, 256K)  │\n│  rxRing      (client → server, 256K)  │\n└───────────────────────────────────────┘\n\n  receiverThread   (reads rxRing)\n  sendMutex        (serializes txRing writes)\n  handlerMutex     (guards RunLoop dispatch)\n  dead flag        (atomic, marks for reaping)\n\n⚠ txRing is SPSC — sendMutex MUST be held\n  for sendResponse() AND sendNotify()",
      "autoResize": true, "fontSize": 12, "fontFamily": 3, "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle", "containerId": "client_conn_box", "lineHeight": 1.25
    },

    {
      "id": "dispatch_box", "type": "rectangle", "x": 60, "y": 520, "width": 400, "height": 120,
      "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#2f9e44", "backgroundColor": "#b2f2bb",
      "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 2, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "index": "a5",
      "roundness": { "type": 3 }, "seed": 6001, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 6002,
      "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": [{"id": "text_dispatch", "type": "text"}],
      "updated": 1774700000000, "link": null, "locked": false
    },
    {
      "id": "text_dispatch", "type": "text", "x": 65, "y": 530, "width": 390, "height": 100,
      "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e", "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "index": "a5a", "roundness": null,
      "seed": 6003, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 6004, "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null, "updated": 1774700000000, "link": null, "locked": false,
      "text": "Dispatch Chain (threaded mode)\n\nreceiverLoop()\n  → recvSignal()           // block until wakeup\n  → readFrame(rxRing)      // read request\n  → onRequest(serviceId, messageId, payload)\n    → handleFoo(args)      // virtual, user implements\n  → sendResponse(txRing)   // write response (holds sendMutex)\n  → sendSignal()           // wake client",
      "originalText": "Dispatch Chain (threaded mode)\n\nreceiverLoop()\n  → recvSignal()           // block until wakeup\n  → readFrame(rxRing)      // read request\n  → onRequest(serviceId, messageId, payload)\n    → handleFoo(args)      // virtual, user implements\n  → sendResponse(txRing)   // write response (holds sendMutex)\n  → sendSignal()           // wake client",
      "autoResize": true, "fontSize": 11, "fontFamily": 3, "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle", "containerId": "dispatch_box", "lineHeight": 1.25
    },

    {
      "id": "rl_loop", "type": "rectangle", "x": 540, "y": 120, "width": 340, "height": 80,
      "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#862e9c", "backgroundColor": "#e5dbff",
      "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 2, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0,
