      "seed": 10003, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 10004, "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null, "updated": 1774700000000, "link": null, "locked": false,
      "text": "sendNotify() — broadcast to all clients\nfor each client:\n  lock sendMutex → writeFrame(txRing) → sendSignal()",
